Here is what the request will look like:

POST https://{assistant.voice.server.url}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messsage": {
    "type": "voice-request",
    "text": "Hello, world!",
    "sampleRate": 24000,
    ...other metadata about the call...
  }
}

